I'll be coming for you.

1004
01:12:44,235 --> 01:12:47,772
Yeah? Will ya?
You promise?

1005
01:12:49,506 --> 01:12:52,010
Oh, yeah. I promise.

1006
01:12:54,045 --> 01:12:55,847
Goddamn it.

1007
