- Open it.
- I'm not playing either.

1070
01:18:12,062 --> 01:18:13,396
- Come on.
- All right.

1071
01:18:14,998 --> 01:18:16,266
Just calm down, all right?

1072
01:18:16,299 --> 01:18:18,101
