wants to kill you.

1135
01:22:48,338 --> 01:22:49,405
Ready?

1136
01:23:20,303 --> 01:23:21,371
Son of a bitch.

1137
01:24:01,511 --> 01:24:02,511
Shane!

1138
01:25:00,269 --> 01:25:01,605
Shane!

1139
01:26:00,764 --> 01:26:03,332
The glass is
bulletproof, asshole.

1140
01:26:03,366 --> 01:26:04,702
Yeah, no shit.

1141
01:26:11,809 --> 01:26:14,477
Well...

1142
