1151
01:26:55,886 --> 01:26:58,756
Slowly. Now!

1152
01:27:00,057 --> 01:27:01,290
All right.

1153
01:27:02,092 --> 01:27:03,627
Get your ass over here.

1154
01:27:09,032 --> 01:27:11,400
