- Okay.

1155
01:27:13,871 --> 01:27:15,639
Don't you try nothing, either.

1156
01:27:17,841 --> 01:27:20,343
Typical hero shit.

1157
01:27:20,376 --> 01:27:22,579
Always wanna be
the savior of others.

1158
01:27:22,613 --> 01:27:23,914
