you would a let us live?

1177
01:28:58,909 --> 01:29:00,476
'Course not.

1178
01:29:01,712 --> 01:29:04,147
That's 'cause you're
a traitorous piece of shit.

1179
01:29:05,082 --> 01:29:08,417
Sticks and stones,
Special Agent Rosa.

1180
01:29:08,451 --> 01:29:09,953
Sticks and stones.

1181
01:29:34,945 --> 01:29:36,546
